{"title_page": "Shorea peltata", "text_new": "{{Speciesbox\n|status = CR\n|status_system = IUCN2.3\n|genus = Shorea\n|species = peltata\n|authority = Sym.\n}}\n\n'''''Shorea peltata''''' (called, along with some other species in the genus ''[[Shorea]]'', '''yellow meranti''') is a species of [[plant]] in the family [[Dipterocarpaceae]]. It is a tree found in [[Sumatra]], [[Peninsular Malaysia]] and [[Borneo]].\n\n==Sources==\n* {{Cite journal | author = Ashton, P. | title = ''Shorea peltata'' | journal = [[The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species]] | volume = 1998 | page = e.T31973A9671665 | publisher = [[IUCN]] | date = 1998 | url = http://www.iucnredlist.org/details/31973/0 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T31973A9671665.en | access-date = 22 December 2017}}\n\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q5490725}}\n\n[[Category:Shorea|peltata]]\n[[Category:Trees of Sumatra]]\n[[Category:Trees of Peninsular Malaysia]]\n[[Category:Trees of Borneo]]\n[[Category:Critically endangered flora of Asia]]\n[[Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot]]\n\n\n{{Dipterocarpaceae-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Speciesbox\n|status = CR\n|status_system = IUCN2.3\n|genus = Shorea\n|species = peltata\n|authority = Sym.\n}}\n\n'''''Shorea peltata''''' (called, along with some other species in the genus ''[[Shorea]]'', '''Yellow Meranti''') is a species of [[plant]] in the family [[Dipterocarpaceae]]. It is a tree found in [[Sumatra]], [[Peninsular Malaysia]] and [[Borneo]].\n\n==Sources==\n* {{Cite journal | author = Ashton, P. | title = ''Shorea peltata'' | journal = [[The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species]] | volume = 1998 | page = e.T31973A9671665 | publisher = [[IUCN]] | date = 1998 | url = http://www.iucnredlist.org/details/31973/0 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T31973A9671665.en | access-date = 22 December 2017}}\n\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q5490725}}\n\n[[Category:Shorea|peltata]]\n[[Category:Trees of Sumatra]]\n[[Category:Trees of Peninsular Malaysia]]\n[[Category:Trees of Borneo]]\n[[Category:Critically end