{"title_page": "Shorea laxa", "text_new": "{{Speciesbox\n|status = CR\n|status_system = IUCN2.3\n|genus = Shorea\n|species = laxa\n|authority = Sloot.\n}}\n\n'''''Shorea laxa''''' (called, along with some other species in the genus ''[[Shorea]]'', '''yellow meranti''') is a species of [[plant]] in the family [[Dipterocarpaceae]]. It is a tree [[endemism|endemic]] to [[Borneo]].\n\n==Sources==\n* {{Cite journal | author = Ashton, P. | title = ''Shorea laxa'' | journal = [[The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species]] | volume = 1998 | page = e.T33421A9782750 | publisher = [[IUCN]] | date = 1998 | url = http://www.iucnredlist.org/details/33421/0 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T33421A9782750.en | access-date = 22 December 2017}}\n\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q5490618}}\n\n[[Category:Shorea|laxa]]\n[[Category:Endemic flora of Borneo]]\n[[Category:Trees of Borneo]]\n[[Category:Critically endangered flora of Asia]]\n[[Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot]]\n\n\n{{Dipterocarpaceae-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Speciesbox\n|status = CR\n|status_system = IUCN2.3\n|genus = Shorea\n|species = laxa\n|authority = Sloot.\n}}\n\n'''''Shorea laxa''''' (called, along with some other species in the genus ''[[Shorea]]'', '''Yellow Meranti''') is a species of [[plant]] in the family [[Dipterocarpaceae]]. It is a tree [[endemism|endemic]] to [[Borneo]].\n\n==Sources==\n* {{Cite journal | author = Ashton, P. | title = ''Shorea laxa'' | journal = [[The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species]] | volume = 1998 | page = e.T33421A9782750 | publisher = [[IUCN]] | date = 1998 | url = http://www.iucnredlist.org/details/33421/0 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T33421A9782750.en | access-date = 22 December 2017}}\n\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q5490618}}\n\n[[Category:Shorea|laxa]]\n[[Category:Endemic flora of Borneo]]\n[[Category:Trees of Borneo]]\n[[Category:Critically endangered flora of Asia]]\n[[Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot]]\n\n\n{{Dipterocarpaceae-stub}}\n", "name_user": "WolfmanSF", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200etop:clean up", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shorea_laxa"}
