sion with [[Guaynabo Fluminense FC]]<ref name=\"https://futbolboricua.co/mucho-flu-para-el-sevilla/ Mucho \u201cFlu\u201d para el Sevilla\">{{cite web |title=Mucho \"Flu\"para el Sevilla |url=https://futbolboricua.co/}}</ref> as a Player/Assistant coach in 2008. He was signed as a Head Coach and General Manager with the [[Miami United]]<ref name=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miami_United_FC\">{{cite web |title=Miami United \"HeadCoach\" |url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miami_United_FC}}</ref> for the (2012/2013 season). \nIn 2014, he started a  '''[[United States Soccer Federation]]''' former U14-16-18 USYMNT) scouting network.<ref name=\"https://www.diez.hn/legionarios/760194-99/ricardo-alcerro-el-cazatalentos-hondure%C3%B1o-al-servicio-de-estados-unidos/ Ricardo Alcerro el cazatalentos al servicio de los Estados Unidos\">{{cite web |title=Ricardo Alcerro \"El Casatalentos de Estados Unidos\" |url=http://www.diez.hn}}</ref> In January 2017, he was named the Director of Football for the  Inter USA Academy.<ref name=\"http://deportetotalusa.com/blog/scuola-calcio-inter-usa-una-opcion-real-de-aprendizaje/\">{{cite web |title=INTER USA ACADEMY \"opcion real de aprendizaje\" |url=http://deportetotalusa.com}}</ref> In July 2018, he was named the club's new Manager.<ref name=\"http://www.elpais.hn/2017/08/21/coach-catracho-inter-usa/ Un Coach Catracho en el Inter USA\">{{cite web |title=Un Coach Catracho en el Inter USA |url=http://www.elpais.hn}}</ref> He also became the new technical advisor at the [https://interusaacademy.org/ Inter Usa Academy].\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://www.diez.hn/legionarios/760194-99/ricardo-alcerro-el-cazatalentos-hondure%C3%B1o-al-servicio-de-estados-unidos/ Ricardo Alcerro casatalentos Hondureno al servicio de Estados unidos]\n*[http://hondusports.com/2016/02/16/antes-de-usar-la-garra-catracha-debemos-manejar-muy-bien-los-conceptos-modernos-del-futbol-ricky-alcerro/ \u201cAntes de usar la garra catracha, debemos manejar muy bien los conceptos modernos del f\u00fatbol\u201d: Ricky Alcerro]\n*[https://www.laprensa.hn/migrantes/hondurenosenestadosunidos/632454-98/seis-hondure%C3%B1os-forman-parte-de-equipo-de-f%C3%BAtbol-de-miami/ \"Hondurenos al Miami United\"]\n*[https://futbolboricua.co/el-fluminense-comienza-sus-preparaciones-en-su-nuevo-hogar/ El Fluminense Firmara Juninho y Ricardo Alcerro ]\n*[[List of Puerto Rico Islanders players|Pr Islanders List of Players]]\n*[https://www.oursportscentral.com/services/releases/battery-deadlocked-by-islanders/n-3050540/ Battery Deadlocked By Islanders]\n*[https://www.oursportscentral.com/services/releases/players-signings-on-the-rise/n-2707910/ USL First Division Signing Players For 2001]\n* [https://www.nacion.com/puro-deporte/real-espana-de-honduras-goleo-8-0-al-real-esteli-de-nicaragua-en-torneo-de-concacaf/EG2QFYTJI5CQLCELH2CLM7SKII/story/ \"Champions League 2000\"]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Alcerro Marad, Ricardo Ahmed}}\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Puerto Rico]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Italy]]\n[[Category:Liga Nacional de F\u00fatbol Profesional de Honduras players]]\n[[Category:Expatriate soccer players in the United States]]\n[[Category:Honduran expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Honduras international footballers]]\n[[Category:Honduran footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Puerto Rico Islanders players]]\n[[Category:New Orleans Storm players]]\n[[Category:1973 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n", "name_user": "Iphone7xx", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ricardo_Alcerro"}
{"title_page": "Shorea multiflora", "text_new": "{{Speciesbox\n|status = LR/lc\n|status_system = IUCN2.3\n|genus = Shorea\n|species = multiflora\n|authority = (Burck) Sym.\n}}\n\n'''''Shorea multiflora''''' (called, along with some other species in the genus ''[[Shorea]]'', '''yellow meranti''') is a species of [[plant]] in the family [[Dipterocarpaceae]]. It is a tree found in [[Sumatra]], [[Peninsular Malaysia]] and [[Borneo]].\n\n==References==\n* {{Cite journal | author = Ashton, P. | title = ''Shorea multiflora'' | journal = [[The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species]] | volume = 1998 | page = e.T33128A9760046 | publisher = [[IUCN]] | date = 1998 | url = http://www.iucnredlist.org/details/33128/0 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T33128A9760046.en | access-date = 22 December 2017}}\n\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q5415649}}\n\n[[Category:Shorea|multiflora]]\n[[Category:Trees of Sumatra]]\n[[Category:Trees of Peninsular Malaysia]]\n[[Category:Trees of Borneo]]\n[[Category:Least concern plants]]\n[[Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot]]\n\n\n{{Dipterocarpaceae-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Speciesbox\n|status = LR/lc\n|status_system = IUCN2.3\n|genus = Shorea\n|species = multiflora\n|authority = (Burck) Sym.\n}}\n\n'''''Shorea multiflora''''' (called, along with some other species in the genus ''[[Shorea]]'', '''Yellow Meranti''') is a species of [[plant]] in the family [[Dipterocarpaceae]]. It is a tree found in [[Sumatra]], [[Peninsular Malaysia]] and [[Borneo]].\n\n==References==\n* {{Cite journal | author = Ashton, P. | title = ''Shorea multiflora'' | journal = [[The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species]] | volume = 1998 | page = e.T33128A9760046 | publisher = [[IUCN]] | date = 1998 | url = http://www.iucnredlist.org/details/33128/0 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T33128A9760046.en | access-date = 22 December 2017}}\n\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q5415649}}\n\n[[Category:Shorea|multiflora]]\n[[Category:Trees of Sumatra]]\n[[Category:Trees of Peninsular Malaysia]]\n[[Category:Tree